Name: Base Station License, Dominicana Radio Dispatcher
Title: A Local Law in relation to the approval of a determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Dominicana Radio Dispatcher, Inc. for the renewal of a license to operate a base station in the borough of Queens.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

      Section one.  The determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Dominicana Radio Dispatcher, Inc. for the renewal of a license to operate a base station at 37-55 108th Street in the borough of Queens is hereby approved. 
      ï¿½2. This local law shall take effect immediately. 

LS#761
07/23/98
